{"tid":865162,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有時揸車真係揸到好燥底","createTime":"2018-10-16T19:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:34:41.000Z","uid":206673,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cdcf825a792d243046c82e9d0e1dd7f851ea97","tid":865162,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"有無試過<br />\n上高速之後一直比㗎車吊住尾，又貼到勁撚埋，好撚親熱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後你放慢佢又慢，你cut線佢又cut，都唔知做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又試過紅綠燈前同隔離線部車並排，一轉綠燈佢就打燈cut去你條線，如果反應慢啲唔踩逼力真係會撞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以揸車真係情商少啲都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5869d911c8aba0d82ec2a67881cc274cfb081d","tid":865162,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T19:47:36.000Z","msg":"暗戀你"},{"pid":"746b03b92993d19f83da731e7a96e34c705a86c7","tid":865162,"uid":167879,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T22:53:08.000Z","msg":"感情瓜葛"},{"pid":"23278339da584a6f2a1f3e695184b5e47a024ca5","tid":865162,"uid":61271,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:18:59.000Z","msg":"掉番轉諗<br />\n<br />\n人地跟你尾推你咪推你囉，又無犯法，你鍾意咪dup重brake收錢囉，使乜躁？<br />\n<br />\n硬cut就真係仆街既，不過都係果句，你無做錯，可以1823佢，一係炒落去等收錢，唔好激親自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dcee6fd591a9ed278e1779cf60062a4175f1c8","tid":865162,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"23278339da584a6f2a1f3e695184b5e47a024ca5","tid":865162,"uid":61271,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:18:59.000Z","msg":"掉番轉諗<br />\n<br />\n人地跟你尾推你咪推你囉，又無犯法，你鍾意咪dup重brake收錢囉，使乜躁？<br />\n<br />\n硬cut就真係仆街既，不過都係果句，你無做錯，可以1823佢，一係炒落去等收錢，唔好激親自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:25:11.000Z","msg":"結